data.title: Artist: Brian McFadden
data.meta_description: Brian McFadden covered Nobody's Fault but Mine, These Arms of Mine, Direct Me, Champagne and Wine and other songs. Brian McFadden originally did Nobody's Fault but Mine, These Arms of Mine, Direct Me, Champagne and Wine and other songs. Brian McFadden wrote Real to Me, Crash and Burn and Together We Are One.
